# Therapy in Central London

The Central London practice offers the same clinical breadth as the Harley Street office in a setting that is accessible from across the city. The same depth of work, the same credentials — integrative and Jungian psychotherapy, EMDR, art therapy, eating disorder treatment, addiction counselling, couples work and executive coaching.

Many clients find that Central London suits their schedule or location better than Harley Street, while others move between the two offices depending on the week. The quality of the work is identical.

## What Is Available

The Central London practice brings together the full range of Dr Jacquet and Associates' clinical disciplines. Integrative and Jungian psychotherapy for the full range of adult presentations. EMDR-trained for over 20 years trauma treatment. Clinical hypnotherapy integrated within psychotherapy. Specialist eating disorder work, including particular expertise in male eating disorders. Addiction counselling informed by Hazelden and Hope-One training. Couples therapy. Executive coaching drawing on ESSEC Business School training.

## Online Therapy

Online therapy is available and is equally effective for most presentations. Many clients work online throughout their therapeutic engagement — whether because of geography, schedule or preference. Online sessions follow the same format and duration as in-person work, and the therapeutic relationship is no less real for being conducted by screen.

